snippet.title: Retro Longplay #026 - Gunlord (Sega Dreamcast)
snippet.description:
This is a full playthrough of the Sega Dreamcast Turrican homage, Gunlord. It's a fairly well made game and if the Turrican name was actually on it, it would fit right in with the best of that series.

Please subscribe if you like gameplay videos.

Check out my main channel at http://www.youtube.com/austinmackert (Reviews, Let's Plays, and more).
